         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne, 5th April 1895. ¶ Circular ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor by direction to inform you that the Government consider that fires should not be regularly used except dur...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.04.05a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Charles Topp</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No.1568, p. 1116, unit 106, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is a circular sent to the heads of 15<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sub-departments within the Chief Secretary's Department, including to the Government Botanist.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The file copy is unsigned, but copies sent out would have been signed by Topp as Under Secretary.</p>
               </note>Chief Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 5th April 1895.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Circular</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor by direction to inform you that the Government consider that fires should not be regularly used except during the months of June, July and August, being lighted in May and September only in exceptionally cold weather, and to request that you will give instructions in your Branch accordingly.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
